Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NDo you know the Girl of White?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,So pure and innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,with a heart as warm\Nas the morning sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.98,Main,,0,0,0,,But there is a Girl\Nof Black as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Cruel and wicked, with a heart\Nas cold as the darkest night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,She burns with jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:34.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Resenting every shining\Nsmile that dances upon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,the cheeks of the Girl of White.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,And eventually, that bitter\Nhatred turns to thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,of erasing her very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hello. Eavesdropping?\N--[FUTASE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NDo you want to hear a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE]\NHuh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:58.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NThe girls I just spoke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,They may be separate, but they\Ncame from the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,To the world of black and white?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE grunts, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, good work you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You're free to go.\NSee you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Come meet me in my\Ndressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Urith--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NNot that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Not with people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,This is our little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NOh, Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know\Nwhat you're in for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:45.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] You're saying Iona\Nis the Girl of Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhat's... happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,So do you know...\Nwhere Fumio ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] That was the last\NI ever saw of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NI hope she's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sighs]\NThis is getting confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,So there's a Girl of Black\Nand maybe she's an LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What does that mean\Nfor the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And is the Girl of White\Nout there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] White...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu didn't tell me\Nanything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'm\Nas confused as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NChiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NIf you gotta pee, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.81,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HITOE gasps]\N--Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NI'm awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] She has these\Nlittle conniption fits
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:33.86,Main,,0,0,0,,from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Just ignore her and carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,So the WIXOSS novel\Nyou wrote is, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.45,Main,,0,0,0,,the symbol of eternal friendship\Nbetween you and Fumio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But it was just\Nan online thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.79,Main,,0,0,0,,when you first\Nstarted, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know much\Nabout being a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,But when I did some research,\NI read that a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,test the waters that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:13.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] To be honest,\NI didn't expect things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,to turn out so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,A touching friendship,\Na happy ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all so cool,\NI could explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] What "happy ending"?!\NThis whole thing is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I wonder what the\Noriginal Fumio is doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN] There's no way\Nfor us to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough to have\Nto go through all this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But then getting out\Nof that card
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.71,Main,,0,0,0,,only to become a Selector again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NBut wait. I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You wrote some books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish granted. You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you still be\Nfighting as a Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's\Nyour wish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a bit ironic\Ncoming from you, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Like how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NIf you're a LRIG now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,that means you were\Na Selector yourself once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You must have had a dream that\Nmeant more to you than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you believed\Nthe words of your LRIG
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.57,Main,,0,0,0,,and counted on her\Nto grant that wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter what kind\Nof miracle it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:07.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hanayo wasn't trying\Nto deceive me on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,She was always\Nlooking out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] Would it be enough\Nif your wish only came true
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,for a short while?\NAfter all you've been through?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] I imagine it's precisely\Nthe sort of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,that would be meaningless\Nif it didn't last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sighs]\NNo... you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NHow about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.53,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how Fumio felt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Being a novelist didn't\Nmean writing one book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:47.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It meant writing them\Nfor her entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Writing only two novels\Ndoesn't give me the right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.66,Main,,0,0,0,,to call myself a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm merely an ephemeral\Nshell of an existence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.75,Main,,0,0,0,,that will fade once\Nthe writing stops
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The wishes that we grant\Nare not mere fleeting fancies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.05,Main,,0,0,0,,They must continue until death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,A miracle forged in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,No escape from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Unlike Fumio, I was neither well\Nread nor particularly creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why my choice of\Nsubject matter is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, my personal story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.02,Main,,0,0,0,,proved interesting\Nenough to sell books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Or it has thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN] But the well of\Nknowledge has since gone dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NYou reached the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why you've got\Nwriter's block, now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's all gonna work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Fueled by the power\Nof friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,her stories will live on in your\Nheart and continue forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NLife isn't a damned book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO "The power\Nof friendship" can't save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NBut I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NI'm not a writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I never was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,But I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] I don't know if\Nit's the promise we made,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,or something built into me,\Nor just a fear of the abyss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,that keeps me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't even know\Nwho the hell I am anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NIf you aren't trapped in a card,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:06.86,Main,,0,0,0,,you're trapped by a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What can you call this\Nexistence, but a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Imprisoned by\Nthe dream of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Forced to struggle\Nfor it as an LRIG
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,and forever after,\Nuntil you lose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] I'm going to\Nthe White Room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to speak\Nwith Mayu again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:26.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Because if I don't, then the\Nstory can't continue, you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.51,Main,,0,0,0,,So who's battling me next, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.68,Main,,0,0,0,,--You?!\N--[CHIYORI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care who,\Nbut let's make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps, whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NI'm not gonna battle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,And neither will Chiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. That's a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that last battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...I can continue\Nthe story after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to write...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN]\NYou understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you think you're\Nacting on some sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.41,Main,,0,0,0,,moral high ground\Nby refusing to battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,--No, that's not what I'm--\N--[ANN] Some people have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,no choice but to do this.\NAnd she's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NThe White Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The giant window...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to write...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...to the White Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NDon't let it upset you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--[CHIYORI sobs]\N--Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] All she ever talks\Nabout are those novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,That must've been\Npretty rough on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one\NI'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]\NYeah, it did kinda shake me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:43.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,She's suffering just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess there're\Nno winners here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if an LRIG\Nbecomes human again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.51,Main,,0,0,0,,they still can't really be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's just another reason\Nfor us to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI'm so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought if everyone\Nknew the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't want\Nto battle anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Like it's that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Not everybody is like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Some Selectors need to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:12.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] No. Fumio's\Na special case, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIt's not just her. Akira, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though the game hurt her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,she needs it to get\Nher confidence back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't say I'm happy\Nto be a Selector,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,but it did let me meet you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHey, come on! Not you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] That doesn't mean\NI want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Every Selector deals with their\Nsuffering in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,But no matter who they\Nare or what they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to stop until I've\Nsaved every one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] That goes for\NFumio and Futase, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's some way\Nto get them back to normal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'm gonna find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona, what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NYou have to find yourself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I became your LRIG\Nbecause I believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I knew\Nyou were strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That meant a lot,\Nand it helped remind me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,of what I need to do\Nto stay on my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.17,Main,,0,0,0,,So, thanks, Ion--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona?! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I) chuckles]\NSuch a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] I owe you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] Oh? Well,\NI'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NActually, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I have another favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] What? I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] It's something\Nthat only you can accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NMm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NSure. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,But, it's her. She'll\Nprobably refuse to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you find what she\Ntreasures most in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] You're smart,\Nyou can figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward\Nto a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] Whatever you do,\Ndon't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[door latches]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI'm home, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:21.07,Main,,0,0,0,,So you are--welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NUh. Hello again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi! It's nice to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NThe Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NThe Girl of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] As I said,\Nyou're the Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] You envy everyone,\Nbring everyone suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You hate everyone,\Nand everyone hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NSuch a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Such a lonely, lonely girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] You're lying.\NI don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Drowning, dripping,\Ndrenched in hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, make them suffer!\NMake them feel your pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NBattling for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Spreading misery to everyone.\NSuch is the fate of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,--the Girl of Black.\N--[IONA] It's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha-What now?\NI think she's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have any medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Wait! How are we\Nsupposed to give it to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThis has never happened to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,so I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIona...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you cold?\NDo you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it a stomach ache, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhy is she acting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] If there's anything\NI can do, just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Why is she\Nso worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Is that why\Nthis hurts so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm cold, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NYou should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the Girl of Black.\NYour body rejects the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,And it rejects you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Longing for white\Nwill only bring you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,more and more suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:28.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But please, be as\Nmiserable as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,She seems to be doing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NIt's tricky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.30,Main,,0,0,0,,...but this\N"Girl of Black" thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.63,Main,,0,0,0,,might be the piece of\Nthe puzzle we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you think Iona's\Nhiding something from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] We'll get some answers\Nout of her when she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe we just need\Nto be her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,That might be the only way\Nto get her to open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYou think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think she\Nwants to trick us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,She probably has a reason\Nfor not talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It was wrong, but, I mean...\NI had things I didn't tell Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so wrapped up\Nin my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't think about what\Nshe was going through at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,And I know that hurt her,\Nso even if Iona's different,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna make\Nthe same mistake twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYou're such a softie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm all like, "We'll get\Nsome answers out of her,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,and now you make me look bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's our second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,And this time, we're all\Nhonest, and we're all friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[knock on door]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NRu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] I don't mean\Nto rain on your parade,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's a bit late. Hitoe's\Nparents might be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. I didn't notice the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I... stay with Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NYeah. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,If I was allowed,\NI'd spend the night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,But I guess I'll see you\Nagain soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We both will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NThis is far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys have Iona\Nto take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NRight. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll call when\NI get home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh--I'd better get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NThat took forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You sure like to keep\Na girl waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NAh. Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] C'mon, Hitoe,\Nlet's have a Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] We haven't done it since\Nwe got our new LRIGs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You scared I'm gonna\Nbeat you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, it's cool!\NWe'll take it slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,So I can torment you\Nall night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.35,Main,,0,0,0,,No, you can't make me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NAw, aren't you tough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if you say no,\NI'll just ask Ru-Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! She doesn't\Nwant to either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:10.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You think I gotta listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone hurt Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it? We've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"Had enough"?\NI'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not push your luck\Nwith me, you little nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,We're not enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We're fighting to save you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you just a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,'Fraid it's gonna take\Na Battle to convince me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[MILULUN] You're wasting your\Ntime--this doofus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,doesn't even have\Nher LRIG with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, I can't sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NWhat? Why the hell not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like you'll have to play\Nplain old WIXOSS instead, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,To hell with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:54.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Ugh, this sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith is counting on me, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,So what happens\Nif I let her dow-- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh god, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,She's gonna hate me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What? I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.63,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll dump me...\NThrow me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I can't...\NI hate this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:15.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] You're smart.\NYou can figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward\Nto a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,--Akira, are you--\N--[AKIRA] Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,There's still a use for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:33.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[thunder cracks]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NIt's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NThe rain's really picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NI hope Hitoe got home okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NIt feels warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:48.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It seemed like you were\Nin a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I see.\NIt wasn't a dream after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NFeeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:08.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it's silly, but you\Nlooked like you were cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,so I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] She does know how\Nan LRIG works, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NMaybe it's Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Uh, Grandma? I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:25.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hitoe--startin' to\Nthink you drowned out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Hitoe can't come\Nto the phone right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,'cause she's not playing nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:32.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NBingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The great detective Ru-Ru\Nsolves another mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhere's Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Shut your mouth\Nand I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:46.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Ahh... Oh.\NYeah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HITOE] No, Ruko!\N--Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NYou will not ruin this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:50.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[crashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira! Stop it!\NI'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, don't hurt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Don't be an idiot\Nlike our little friend here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.11,Main,,0,0,0,,and forget your LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want Iona\Nto miss out on the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:00.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,...Iona can't really--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NGet your ass over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,--[line clicks]\N--[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she get soaked or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:19.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira took Hitoe hostage,\Nand she wants me to bring Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NFine. We'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NAnd have you go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I'm better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[thunder crakcs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[thunder cracks]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be a drama queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I had to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, she bit my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do\Nfor my next photo shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYou're the one who started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA snarls]\NThis is a pain for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for\Nnot being with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, where's Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI see you've sunk to a new low.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys missed quite\Nthe show, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe was acting all hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"I won't let anyone hurt Ruko!"\NAnd then I kicked her ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HITOE grunts]\N--Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't have these little nerds\Ngetting any big ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to\Nbattle me that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.42,Main,,0,0,0,,then let's get it over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,But after I win, you're\Ngonna stop this for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NThat's cute and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,but I don't think you\Nunderstand the situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The rain kept me.\NI hope I'm not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NHow unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.09,0:23:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What a letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,And besides, where's\Nthe fun in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It might not be my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"That Lie, a Scar".
